data.description: Super cutie in the family friendly community of Woodcreek! CORNER LOT! 3 bedrooms and 2 full bath! Secondary beds are separate from the spacious primary suite which has a large shower and walk in closet! Nice size kitchen with center island that is perfect for serving meals and accommodates extra seating! Open to the dining and living area. Hard surface flooring in the main areas making it easy to clean! Nice size backyard with covered patio! This community has great amenities which include 3 swimming pools, dog park, catch and release pond and a clubhouse! This home is perfect for the first time home buyer or a family wanting to downsize! Great location - right by the city hall and public park-splash pad. Here is HOME!
